{
  "title": "Dorothea & Annette Support Rank A+",
  "script": [
    {
      "character": "Dorothea",
      "dialogue": "♪ I met him in the winter… He loved me in the spring… ♪",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "dorothea",
        "expression": "happy"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Annette",
      "dialogue": "♪ We married in midsummer… A gift each season brings… ♪",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "annette",
        "expression": ""
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Villager 1",
      "dialogue": "Woohoo! Dorothea!",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "npc",
        "character": "man2"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Villager 2",
      "dialogue": "The girl who’s singing with her… What was her name again?",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "npc",
        "character": "woman2"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Villager 1",
      "dialogue": "I think it was Annette.",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "npc",
        "character": "man2"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Dorothea",
      "dialogue": "♪ And though my sorrow’s moved the earth— I have no use for the dirt— ♪",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "dorothea"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Annette",
      "dialogue": "♪ I only want that shining one— who promised me “until oblivion…”♪",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "annette"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Villager 2",
      "dialogue": "Their voices really complement each other.",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "npc",
        "character": "woman2"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Dorothea",
      "dialogue": "That’s all we have for now! Thank you for listening!",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "dorothea",
        "expression": "happy"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Annette",
      "dialogue": "So many people… Did I really just do that?",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "annette",
        "expression": "blushing"
      }
    },

    {
      "dialogue": "A short while later…"
    },

    {
      "character": "Dorothea",
      "dialogue": "Ah… It’s nice to perform again, even for something small.",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "dorothea",
        "expression": "happy"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Annette",
      "dialogue": "Small? I know you’re used to singing in a big opera house, but that was still an impressive crowd. The audience was really cheering for you.",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "annette",
        "expression": "surprised"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Dorothea",
      "dialogue": "Not just me, Annette.",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "dorothea"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Annette",
      "dialogue": "Come on. We all know they wouldn’t have shown up if you hadn’t been here.",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "annette"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Dorothea",
      "dialogue": "That’s quite enough. Would a refined lady be so quick to dismiss her own talents? I think not.",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "dorothea"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Village Girl",
      "dialogue": "Um… Excuse me…?",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "npc",
        "character": "girl"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Annette",
      "dialogue": "Oh, hello! Were you watching just now?",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "annette",
        "expression": "surprised"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Village Girl",
      "dialogue": "I was.",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "npc",
        "character": "girl"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Dorothea",
      "dialogue": "Hang on. I recognize that face. You’re that girl I sang to five years ago, aren’t you?",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "dorothea",
        "expression": "surprised"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Village Girl",
      "dialogue": "Yes! I’m surprised you remember me.",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "npc",
        "character": "girl"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Dorothea",
      "dialogue": "I could never forget such an adorable, kind girl. Or the day I made an important friend.",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "dorothea",
        "expression": "winking"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Annette",
      "dialogue": "Wait, are you talking about me?",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "annette",
        "expression": "surprised"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Dorothea",
      "dialogue": "Of course! We might not have gotten to know each other so well if you hadn’t helped me escape that crowd.",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "dorothea",
        "expression": "happy"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Annette",
      "dialogue": "Hehe. I suppose you have a point.",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "annette",
        "expression": "happy"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Village Girl",
      "dialogue": "Your name is Annette, right?",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "npc",
        "character": "girl"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Annette",
      "dialogue": "Yup! What can I do for you?",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "annette"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Village Girl",
      "dialogue": "I… wanted you to have these, as a token of my appreciation.",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "npc",
        "character": "girl"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Annette",
      "dialogue": "Oh my goodness, flowers! They’re beautiful! Thank you.",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "annette",
        "expression": "blushing"
      }
    },

    {
      "dialogue": "Village girl exits"
    },

    {
      "character": "Annette",
      "dialogue": "Wow…",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "annette",
        "expression": "blushing"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Dorothea",
      "dialogue": "How are you enjoying your taste of fame? Should we plan another show?",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "dorothea",
        "expression": "winking"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Annette",
      "dialogue": "I’ll have to think about it. Remembering all those people we had to run from way back when is making me exhausted all over again.",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "annette"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Dorothea",
      "dialogue": "I suppose the life of a performer isn’t for everyone. But I’m glad I got to sing with you at least once. I’ve actually wanted to do that since our academy days.",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "dorothea"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Annette",
      "dialogue": "You have? Why didn’t you just—actually, never mind. We both know I would’ve been too nervous to accept.",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "annette"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Dorothea",
      "dialogue": "My thoughts exactly. Imagine my surprise when you asked me to sing with you! And it went like a dream, too.",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "dorothea",
        "expression": "happy"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Dorothea",
      "dialogue": "By the way, before I forget: do you have those earrings on you right now?",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "dorothea"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Annette",
      "dialogue": "Oh, right! I promised I’d try them on after we sang, didn’t I? Here I go…",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "annette",
        "expression": "happy"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Annette",
      "dialogue": "Okay. How do they look?",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "annette",
        "expression": "blushing"
      }
    },

    {
      "character": "Dorothea",
      "dialogue": "Perfect, Annette. Absolutely perfect.",
      "portrait": {
        "type": "war",
        "character": "dorothea",
        "expression": "blushing"
      }
    },

    {
      "dialogue": "Dorothea and Annette have reached Support Rank A+."
    }
  ]
}
